show.description: Rajat, a humble and loyal boy, whom his ambitious girlfriend publicly embarrassed and left him due to lack of status and money, returns to India. But everyone is shocked when they find out that he is the husband of the beautiful and powerful CEO of the country's biggest company. Watch "Revenge of My Fake Boyfriend" - a unique story of love, betrayal and hatred!
